#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_html/about.html.heex:67
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "We believe openness builds better tools, keeping only what’s needed closed for sustainable development."
msgstr "私たちは、オープンネスがより良いツールを生み、持続可能な開発のために必要な部分だけを閉ざすと信じています。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_html/about.html.heex:109
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "We embrace standards for long-term success while respecting freedom of choice."
msgstr "私たちは選択の自由を尊重しつつ、長期的な成功のために標準を受け入れます。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_controller.ex:613
#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_html/pricing.html.heex:664
