#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_html/pricing.html.heex:443
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Yes, we do. Please contact us at contact@tuist.dev to discuss your team's needs and we'll set up a custom plan that works for you."
msgstr "はい、対応しています。contact@tuist.devまでご連絡いただき、チームのニーズをご相談ください。最適なカスタムプランを設定します。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_html/pricing.html.heex:692
